name: Family of the dead T-Shirt

Please state what size you require when ordering.

name: Tales That Start With A Whisper European Tour edition 2013
description:
Thirteen Shots and Arkham Records proudly presents 
'Tales That Start With A Whisper European Tour Edition'
The critically acclaimed second album has now been extended to feature the Horror-Punks.com nominated 'Vaudeville' so now you can enjoy both albums without chancing the CD. 
The running order is 
(1) Death Jam 2000
(2) Zombies From The USSR
(3) Bewitched
(4) Psychojuke Box
(5) Get In my Crypt
(6) Nekrosexual 
(7) Tales That Start With A Whisper
(8) Miss Eerie
(9) Inspector George 
(10) Boogie Man 
(11) Danzig
(12) This a Looks Like A Job For Batman
(13) Graveyard Stomp

This new packaging comes with a new back cover 
The disk is a Black vinyl CD with the 'Vaudeville' art work printed on.
